  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Restaurant &amp; Bar</span></strong></p>
<p><strong>Benedicta</strong> <strong>R</strong><strong>estaurant</strong> boasts three Michelin forks. and has an ever changing menu with seasonal flavours complemented by a superb wine list.</p>
<p><strong>Garden Bar</strong> offers a refreshing aperitif or delicious cocktail created by one of the resident mixologists. The bar is open daily from 4.30pm until midnight. </p>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Pool</span></strong></p>
<p>Nestled in the internal courtyard gardens you'll find an amply sized Jacuzzi measuring 20m². Heated to a constant 36<span>°c, this is the ideal spot to kick back, rest any weary feet from a day of exploring the town or just take a day for yourself to relax in the Tuscan sunshine.</span></p>]]></facilityDescription>
