  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Comfort Rooms </strong>sleep two people and offer a peaceful and homely space with either parquet or carpeted flooring. Amenities include en suite bathroom with bath or shower, toiletries, hairdryer, towel warmer, air conditioning, minibar and free wifi.</p>
<p><strong>Premium Rooms </strong>renovated in 2017 sleep two people and are furnished beautifully with classic furniture, calming hues and modern fabrics. From here you can enjoy views of the ancient Franciscan Cloister or the ambient streets of Florence. Coffee facilities are also available in this room. </p>
<p><strong>Double Rooms with balcony</strong> sleep two and are the perfect choice if you're looking for a romantic break. With views out onto the internal gardens and a balcony with furniture, perfect for enjoying a morning coffee or just watching the world go by, these spacious and elegantly decorated rooms are some of the best the Rivoli Boutique has to offer. Signature toiletries are on offer with this room type which can also be set up with twin beds if you prefer. </p>
<p><strong>Family Rooms </strong>can sleep three to four and are a great option if you're travelling with family or friends. Triple rooms are available with a double bed and sofa bed or larger rooms which can take up to four are composed of two separate bedrooms (a double and a further bedroom with sofa bed). Enjoy tea &amp; coffee making facilities as well as mineral water on arrival and views out onto the streets or courtyard. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
